description: AMUNDI MSCI SWITZERLAND UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI Switzerland Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to around 40 leading stocks on the Swiss market, with a single transaction. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi MSCI Switzerland UCITS ETF - EUR (C)
